'''Zoltán Teszári''' ({{IPA-hu|ˈzoltaːn ˈtɛsaːri}}; born 1970 in [[Oradea]]) is a [[Romania]]n [[Information technology|IT]] [[entrepreneur]]. According to [[Forbes|Forbes Romania]], he is one of the richest entrepreneurs in the country, and the richest [[Hungarians in Romania|ethnic Hungarian]] with a [[net worth]] of 370 million [[EUR]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.maszol.ro/index.php/gazdasag/19799-teszari-zoltan-a-leggazdagabb-romaniai-magyar-uzletember|title=Teszári Zoltán a leggazdagabb romániai magyar üzletember|publisher=Új Magyar Szó|date=25 October 2013|accessdate=1 March 2013|language=Hungarian}}</ref> He controls the largest cable television and [[Internet service provider]] in Romania, [[RCS&RDS]].<ref>[http://www.wall-street.ro/slideshow/IT-C-Tehnologie/73140/Ce-masuri-au-luat-RCS-RDS-UPC-si-Romtelecom-pentru-a-trece-de-criza.html#slide_title Ce masuri au luat RCS&RDS, UPC si Romtelecom pentru a trece de criza?]</ref>

